#  Plant-IA

[![PyPI version](https://img.shields.io/pypi/v/plant-ia?label=pypi)](https://pypi.org/project/plant-ia/)
![Tests](https://github.com/DISTinTheHouse/plant-ia/actions/workflows/tests.yml/badge.svg)
